snippet.title: Deathbound - Official Steel and Magic Teaser Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description:
Take a peek at brutal combat, including magic-based fighting and weapon attacks, in this latest trailer for Deathbound. 

Deathbound is an upcoming Soulslike action RPG set in a world where Faith and Science clash. Absorb the essences of fallen warriors to harness their powers and abilities. Survive in a brutal reality where Life and Death were never more conflicted.

Deathbound will be available on PC.
